('c2000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005','ASRock B550M Pro4','asrock-b550m-pro4','MOBO-ASR-B550M-PRO4','b1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000052','a1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002','ASRock','B550M Pro4',360000,400000,12,'Tarjeta madre Micro-ATX AM4 DDR4 ideal para builds Ryzen 5 económicos.','La ASRock B550M Pro4 es la elección inteligente para builds AM4 compactos y asequibles. Soporte para Ryzen 5000 y anteriores, con DDR4, PCIe 4.0 y conectividad completa.','{"socket":"AM4","form_factor":"Micro-ATX","ram_slots":4,"ram_type":["DDR4"],"max_ram":128,"chipset":"B550","m2_slots":2,"pcie_version":"4.0"}','{"amd","am4","ddr4","micro-atx","entrada","oferta"}',true,false),

('c2000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006','MSI MAG B550 Tomahawk','msi-mag-b550-tomahawk','MOBO-MSI-B550-TOMAHAWK','b1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000052','a1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002','MSI','MAG B550 Tomahawk',520000,NULL,9,'Tarjeta madre ATX AM4 con diseño gaming robusto y excelente VRM para Ryzen 5000.','La MSI MAG B550 Tomahawk es una de las tarjetas madre AM4 más recomendadas por su relación calidad/precio. VRM sólido para Ryzen 9, 2 ranuras M.2, PCIe 4.0 y diseño gaming sin LED RGB excesivo.','{"socket":"AM4","form_factor":"ATX","ram_slots":4,"ram_type":["DDR4"],"max_ram":128,"chipset":"B550","m2_slots":2,"pcie_version":"4.0"}','{"amd","am4","ddr4","atx","gaming","mid-range"}',true,true);

